snippet.title: Namor Attacks Wakanda | Black Panther: Wakanda Forever (2022) Movie Clip HD
snippet.description:
Namor attacks Wakanda by flooding the Golden City, sparking an epic fight scene between Wakandans and the Talokanil. This movie clip is from Black Panther: Wakanda Forever (2022). The Wakandans Will Return In Avengers: Doomsday.
